show.description: After losing everything to her cheating husband, Tasha finds unexpected kindness from a taxi driver named Ken. Though fate pulls them apart, Ken keeps returning — and a deep romance begins to bloom. But behind his gentle smile lies a secret: Ken is the son of a mafia boss, chasing shadows from his past.
